00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:01,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure it bothers him that 
he can't perform torture.</font>

165
00:08:03,980 --> 00:08:08,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is not being able to torture 
really something to worry about?</i></font>

166
00:08:05,080 --> 00:08:08,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}...a-alone.</font>

167
00:08:09,090 --> 00:08:11,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, I wasn't listening. 
Could you say that again?</font>

168
00:08:11,410 --> 00:08:13,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're kidding me.</font>

169
00:08:15,390 --> 00:08:16,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're done?</font>

170
00:08:16,660 --> 00:08:17,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

171
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:19,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a horrible smell.</font>

172
00:08:20,070 --> 00:08:22,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got a bit rough because of the rush,</font>

173
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:24,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I only just finished, so...</font>

174
00:08:28,060 --> 00:08:28,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, boy.</font>

175
00:08:32,680 --> 00:08:35,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh. This couldn't get any worse.</font>

176
00:08:37,630 --> 00:08:40,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He really just puked on 
me and then fainted...</font>

177
00:08:40,790 --> 00:08:42,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got his own clothes dirty, too.</font>

178
00:08:52,540 --> 00:08:54,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where am I?!</font>

179
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The nap room.</font>

180
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:56,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

181
00:08:56,860 --> 00:08:59,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because you barfed, duh.</font>

182
00:09:00,180 --> 00:09:01,720
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#19141a">GLOOM</font></b></font>

183
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:05,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You think I'm pathetic, don't you?</font>

184
00:09:05,160 --> 00:09:05,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup.</font>

185
00:09:07,690 --> 00:09:11,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you blame me? I mean, 
I'll never react like you do.</font>

186
00:09:12,140 --> 00:09:14,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's it matter what I think, anyway?</font>

187
00:09:15,550 --> 00:09:18,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no need for you to think 
the same about yourself.</font>

188
00:09:18,780 --> 00:09:21,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But since you puked on me 
and made me take care of you</font>

189
00:09:21,980 --> 00:09:24,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">after making me work overtime, 
you should be thanking me until you die.</font>

190
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:29,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Thanks.</font>

191
00:09:30,230 --> 00:09:32,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all about being the 
right person for the job.</font>

192
00:09:32,520 --> 00:09:35,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't stress over it 
so much. It's annoying.</font>

193
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:39,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hela-san and Siu-san 
really care about you,</font>

194
00:09:39,620 --> 00:09:41,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and everyone around you relies on you.</font>

195
00:09:44,390 --> 00:09:45,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

196
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:48,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you rely on me, too?</font>

197
00:09:48,680 --> 00:09:50,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no, not me.</font>

198
00:09:51,170 --> 00:09:53,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you're always... always...</font>

199
00:09:59,830 --> 00:10:01,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You glare at him every time you meet.</i></font>

200
00:10:02,340 --> 00:10:04,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should be able to 
handle it better than that.</font>

201
00:10:06,090 --> 00:10:09,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's used to you guys, 
so it doesn't matter,</font>

202
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:14,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but with other people, he's always 
keeping his distance and cowering.</font>

203
00:10:14,610 --> 00:10:16,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's gotta be exhausting 
for all parties.</font>

204
00:10:17,380 --> 00:10:20,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why it's good to have 
a guy like me around.</font>

205
00:10:20,910 --> 00:10:22,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really are a mean one, aren't you?</font>

206
00:10:32,190 --> 00:10:36,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sero-san, a lot of the criminals you two 
handle committed horrific crimes, right?</font>

207
00:10:37,190 --> 00:10:39,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doesn't it ever make 
you want to kill them?</font>

208
00:10:39,690 --> 00:10:40,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

209
00:10:41,090 --> 00:10:45,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're all revolting, 
but it's not our place to kill them.</font>

210
00:10:45,920 --> 00:10:47,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Personal feelings have 
no place in torture.</font>

211
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:56,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which one do you want to hear about?</font>

212
00:10:56,260 --> 00:10:58,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The first one, the preschooler?</font>

213
00:10:59,150 --> 00:11:00,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The second, the salaryman?</font>

214
00:11:01,670 --> 00:11:03,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or my third, the high school girl?</font>

215
00:11:12,900 --> 00:11:14,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, man.</font>

216
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:17,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I did get the 
necessary info, though.</font>

217
00:11:23,150 --> 00:11:26,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry. I messed up.</font>

218
00:11:26,800 --> 00:11:28,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Again?! You—</font>

219
00:11:39,420 --> 00:11:41,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Handle your job better.</font>

220
00:11:43,550 --> 00:11:45,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I handle it fine.</font>

221
00:11:45,560 --> 00:11:46,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How is this fine?</font>

222
00:11:48,810 --> 00:11:49,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

223
00:11:51,460 --> 00:11:55,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll overlook it today and today only. 
Now my debt's paid off.</font>

224
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:56,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your debt?</font>

225
00:11:57,400 --> 00:12:00,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you mean from when 
you barfed all over me?</font>

226
00:12:00,520 --> 00:12:02,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are just so...</font>

227
00:12:02,990 --> 00:12:05,990
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an8}<b><font size="35"><font color="#fefefe">The <font color="#ede33a">D<font color="#fefefe">aily <font color="#ede33a">L<font color="#fefefe">ife of a <font color="#9513eb">P<font color="#fefefe">art-Time <font color="#9513eb">T<font color="#fefefe">orturer</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

228
00:12:05,990 --> 00:12:08,990
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an8}<b><font size="35"><font color="#0b0a0c">The <font color="#f0a735">D<font color="#0b0a0c">aily <font color="#57d538">L<font color="#0b0a0c">ife of a <font color="#69586e">P<font color="#0b0a0c">art-Time <font color="#9513eb">T<font color="#0b0a0c">orturer</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

229
00:12:16,510 --> 00:12:17,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hela-san, this is for you.</font>

230
00:12:18,460 --> 00:12:19,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

231
00:12:20,310 --> 00:12:21,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about now?</font>

232
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:23,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just a little more.</font>

233
00:12:23,920 --> 00:12:25,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it good?</font>

234
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:26,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is!</font>

235
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:28,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Papa, open wide!</font>

236
00:12:31,330 --> 00:12:34,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey there! You boys!</font>

237
00:12:35,420 --> 00:12:38,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're just two lonely women over here.</font>

238
00:12:38,180 --> 00:12:40,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want to hang out with us?</font>

239
00:12:41,560 --> 00:12:44,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Papa, who are these people?</font>

240
00:12:44,200 --> 00:12:45,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No idea.</font>

241
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:47,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Papa, don't go with them!</font>

242
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:48,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Papa"?</font>

243
00:12:48,590 --> 00:12:49,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kids?</font>

244
00:12:49,830 --> 00:12:51,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Two papas?</font>

245
00:12:51,370 --> 00:12:54,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sorry for bothering you!</font>

246
00:12:54,280 --> 00:12:57,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nero-chan, you're so smart! 
You make Papa very happy!</font>

247
00:12:58,920 --> 00:13:00,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't get to call yourself that.</font>

248
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:03,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so cold!</font>

249
00:13:03,570 --> 00:13:06,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's great that those two 
could come along, isn't it?</font>

250
00:13:06,430 --> 00:13:09,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hela was nice enough to 
say to bring them along.</font>

251
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:12,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Both of you, say thank you to Hela.</font>

252
00:13:12,800 --> 00:13:14,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

253
00:13:14,940 --> 00:13:17,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Uncle Hela!</font>

254
00:13:17,690 --> 00:13:19,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean "Big Sister."</font>

255
00:13:19,920 --> 00:13:22,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Uncle.</font>

256
00:13:19,920 --> 00:13:22,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Thank you, Hela-san!</font>

257
00:13:22,780 --> 00:13:24,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will dock your pay.</font>

258
00:13:26,990 --> 00:13:28,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noe, you should go and have fun, too.</font>

259
00:13:28,910 --> 00:13:30,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm having more than enough fun h—</font>

260
00:13:31,740 --> 00:13:33,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't have enough people, 
so get over here!</font>

261
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:36,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn that Sero...</font>

262
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:38,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do your best out there!</font>

263
00:13:41,550 --> 00:13:43,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rock, paper, scissors!</font>

264
00:13:46,020 --> 00:13:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't drag me down.</font>

265
00:13:47,730 --> 00:13:49,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Same to you.</font>

266
00:13:49,050 --> 00:13:50,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here we go!</font>

267
00:13:50,500 --> 00:13:51,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

268
00:13:55,270 --> 00:13:56,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

269
00:13:56,680 --> 00:13:58,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What are you doing?!</font>

270
00:13:58,600 --> 00:14:00,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And what are you, a statue?!</font>

271
00:14:02,040 --> 00:14:04,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hugh is dangerous. We'll aim for Mike.</font>

272
00:14:04,990 --> 00:14:06,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

273
00:14:07,780 --> 00:14:08,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sero!</font>

274
00:14:09,030 --> 00:14:10,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it!</font>

275
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:12,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sero-san!</font>

276
00:14:13,020 --> 00:14:16,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't hit the scary ball at me.</font>

277
00:14:24,250 --> 00:14:27,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm weak against adorable 
creatures, okay?!</font>

278
00:14:27,490 --> 00:14:30,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could hit thousands of balls 
at full force against Noe, though!</font>

279
00:14:30,840 --> 00:14:32,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You little...</font>

280
00:14:32,310 --> 00:14:35,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mike's Super Cutie Attack!</font>

281
00:14:35,400 --> 00:14:37,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup! That's damn cute!</font>

282
00:14:37,030 --> 00:14:39,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The kids sure are enjoying themselves.</font>

283
00:14:39,780 --> 00:14:43,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, when someone who's enjoying 
himself just as much says so...</font>

284
00:14:43,780 --> 00:14:45,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not enjoying anything.</font>

285
00:14:45,780 --> 00:14:49,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You invited us all to hang out 
like this out of nowhere.</font>

286
00:14:46,860 --> 00:14:48,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You have some on you!</font>

287
00:14:49,280 --> 00:14:50,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on?</font>

288
00:14:50,580 --> 00:14:52,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, nothing's going on.</font>

289
00:14:53,470 --> 00:14:56,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not plotting anything, are you?</font>

290
00:14:56,010 --> 00:14:59,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop saying things that 
make me sound so awful!</font>

291
00:15:00,430 --> 00:15:02,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When it was just us two, 
it was good that way.</font>

292
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:07,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's not so bad having 
everyone together like this, is it?</font>

293
00:15:09,170 --> 00:15:10,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm happy for you!</font>

294
00:15:10,730 --> 00:15:13,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since Sero-kun and everyone came, 
you seem like you're having fun!</font>

295
00:15:13,620 --> 00:15:15,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Both Papa and Hela-chan!</font>

296
00:15:15,800 --> 00:15:18,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just wondering, but 
why call me "Hela-chan"?</font>

297
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:20,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's shorter than "Uncle Hela"!</font>

298
00:15:22,560 --> 00:15:24,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose I'll take it.</font>

299
00:15:32,460 --> 00:15:34,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Papa, hurry up and light it!</font>

300
00:15:34,880 --> 00:15:36,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Light it!</font>

301
00:15:36,180 --> 00:15:38,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay back. This is dangerous.</font>

302
00:15:38,200 --> 00:15:40,060
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font size="20"><font color="#eef0f2">Hugh</font></font></font>

303
00:15:41,400 --> 00:15:42,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look! Look!</font>

304
00:15:42,750 --> 00:15:46,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're getting all excited 
like little kids. It's adorable.</i></font>

305
00:15:46,390 --> 00:15:47,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Hugh!</font>

306
00:15:48,210 --> 00:15:49,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we changed the amount of powder,</font>

307
00:15:49,720 --> 00:15:51,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">do you think we could 
use them for torture?</font>

308
00:15:51,620 --> 00:15:52,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That might just work!</font>

309
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:55,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're so cute.</i></font>

310
00:15:56,680 --> 00:15:58,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall we start heading home?</font>

311
00:15:58,660 --> 00:16:00,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

312
00:16:00,130 --> 00:16:01,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did everyone have fun?</font>

313
00:16:01,980 --> 00:16:03,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was tons of fun!</font>

314
00:16:03,920 --> 00:16:05,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had fun!</font>

315
00:16:05,460 --> 00:16:07,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you!</font>

316
00:16:07,030 --> 00:16:08,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad to hear it.</font>

317
00:16:08,380 --> 00:16:12,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now you'll be able to do your best 
at work tomorrow, right?</font>

318
00:16:12,560 --> 00:16:14,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've accepted a very important case.</font>

319
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:19,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

320
00:16:19,150 --> 00:16:20,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew it.</font>

321
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:31,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hela-san said it was 
a very important case.</font>

322
00:16:31,850 --> 00:16:34,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure none of it will come 
to us, though, right?</font>

323
00:16:34,930 --> 00:16:36,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, that's true.</font>

324
00:16:39,400 --> 00:16:42,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've got four torture targets this time.</font>

325
00:16:43,200 --> 00:16:45,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So the four of us will take it on.</font>

326
00:16:45,560 --> 00:16:49,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cool! This is the first time all four 
of us have worked at the same time!</font>

327
00:16:49,920 --> 00:16:51,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't get so excited.</font>

328
00:16:51,880 --> 00:16:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These guys have done abductions, 
murder, human trafficking...</font>

329
00:16:55,800 --> 00:16:59,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're a hardcore criminal 
organization that'll do anything!</font>

330
00:16:59,460 --> 00:17:03,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And this time, we have core 
members of their organization.</font>

331
00:17:03,140 --> 00:17:05,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we take them down, 
we might get closer to their leader.</font>

332
00:17:06,050 --> 00:17:08,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a big job.</font>

333
00:17:08,150 --> 00:17:10,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it's a big job, then...</font>

334
00:17:11,490 --> 00:17:13,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">do you think we'll get bonuses?</font>

335
00:17:14,300 --> 00:17:15,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Probably.</font>

336
00:17:15,720 --> 00:17:17,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

337
00:17:17,480 --> 00:17:21,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... want to give my mom 
and dad a trip as a present.</font>

338
00:17:21,840 --> 00:17:23,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What a good kid!</i></font>

339
00:17:25,260 --> 00:17:29,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The one I'm in charge of says the 
lead criminal is a man called Sakoru.</font>

340
00:17:29,940 --> 00:17:32,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The one I'm in charge 
of says it's Sakoru, too.</font>

341
00:17:32,150 --> 00:17:33,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Same here.</font>

342
00:17:33,520 --> 00:17:34,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Same.</font>

343
00:17:35,010 --> 00:17:38,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right! Everyone matches!</font>

344
00:17:38,800 --> 00:17:40,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which means...</font>

345
00:17:40,480 --> 00:17:42,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they've all agreed on the 
same story ahead of time.</font>

346
00:17:42,870 --> 00:17:44,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

347
00:17:44,280 --> 00:17:45,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought so.</font>

348
00:17:45,540 --> 00:17:48,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And they keep babbling on 
about stuff we never asked about.</font>

349
00:17:49,060 --> 00:17:52,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's likely that most of this 
follows their script,</font>

350
00:17:52,380 --> 00:17:54,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but there are small differences.</font>

351
00:17:54,280 --> 00:17:55,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's unskillfully done.</font>

352
00:17:55,570 --> 00:17:58,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll try shaking them up 
to trick them into spilling.</font>

353
00:17:58,270 --> 00:18:00,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You haven't tortured yours 
at all yet, have you?</font>

354
00:18:00,440 --> 00:18:02,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The interrogation was 
the important part, so...</font>

355
00:18:02,720 --> 00:18:05,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no need to hold back. 
I'll leave it to you.</font>

356
00:18:05,230 --> 00:18:06,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

357
00:18:06,430 --> 00:18:10,400
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>{\an7}<font color="#de4a5b">Torture <font color="#4b4b4b">builds a sustainable society</font></font></b></font></font>

358
00:18:06,430 --> 00:18:10,400
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>{\an8}<font color="#de4a5b">Give the villains 
the <font color="#9a4f59">iron hammer</font></font></b></font></font>

359
00:18:07,380 --> 00:18:10,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, let's get back to it.</font>

360
00:18:10,590 --> 00:18:11,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Let's give it our best!</font>

361
00:18:11,350 --> 00:18:13,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know what you said back there,</font>

362
00:18:11,680 --> 00:18:12,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yeah!</font>

363
00:18:14,270 --> 00:18:16,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but you already got accurate 
info out of yours, right?</font>

364
00:18:16,820 --> 00:18:17,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

365
00:18:17,790 --> 00:18:20,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The lead criminal's a guy named Try.</font>

366
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:21,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

367
00:18:21,770 --> 00:18:24,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you got that out of yours, too, huh?</font>

368
00:18:24,130 --> 00:18:25,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup.</font>

369
00:18:25,240 --> 00:18:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You gave those two the tougher 
ones on purpose, didn't you?</font>

370
00:18:29,210 --> 00:18:31,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hela said to do it that way.</font>

371
00:18:31,600 --> 00:18:34,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. In that case...</font>

372
00:18:35,140 --> 00:18:37,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wanna bet on whether 
those two can do it or not?</font>

373
00:18:37,730 --> 00:18:40,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You love this stuff, don't you? Fine.</font>

374
00:18:40,160 --> 00:18:41,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They can.</font>

375
00:18:42,560 --> 00:18:44,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This isn't even a bet!</font>

376
00:18:44,970 --> 00:18:46,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you change yours.</font>

377
00:18:46,590 --> 00:18:48,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? I don't wanna!</font>

378
00:18:49,720 --> 00:18:51,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you mean that lot?</font>

379
00:18:51,310 --> 00:18:53,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry. We're getting the job done.</font>

380
00:18:54,980 --> 00:18:57,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me? Oh, no, no.</font>

381
00:18:57,440 --> 00:19:00,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu, Sero, and our two rookies.</font>

382
00:19:00,360 --> 00:19:01,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Rookies?</i></font>

383
00:19:01,400 --> 00:19:03,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is a big case for us, you know.</i></font>

384
00:19:03,480 --> 00:19:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, yes.</font>

385
00:19:04,280 --> 00:19:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Leaving it to rookies is—</i></font>

386
00:19:04,880 --> 00:19:07,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, be quiet! Don't 
underestimate our rookies!</font>

387
00:19:09,230 --> 00:19:11,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The police inspector's griping again?</font>

388
00:19:11,420 --> 00:19:12,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

389
00:19:12,590 --> 00:19:14,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He worries far too much.</font>

390
00:19:14,590 --> 00:19:18,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought the task might be a 
little too difficult for them, too.</font>

391
00:19:18,910 --> 00:19:20,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is, a little.</font>

392
00:19:21,390 --> 00:19:23,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if I know those two, they'll be fine.</font>

393
00:19:23,530 --> 00:19:27,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, they look so cute when they're 
struggling over a tough challenge.</font>

394
00:19:28,290 --> 00:19:29,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're being mean.</font>

395
00:19:29,850 --> 00:19:31,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is just love!</font>

396
00:19:35,350 --> 00:19:37,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I know that what he's saying is a lie,</i></font>

397
00:19:38,490 --> 00:19:40,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I can't get the truth out of him.</i></font>

398
00:19:46,240 --> 00:19:48,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is the first time 
I've had this much trouble.</i></font>

399
00:19:49,470 --> 00:19:53,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I never knew long torture 
sessions were so exhausting.</i></font>

400
00:19:55,340 --> 00:19:57,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm losing my strength and intensity.</i></font>

401
00:19:57,840 --> 00:20:01,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I guess someone like me really 
can't be like Sero-san and—</i></font>

402
00:20:01,570 --> 00:20:02,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mike-kun.</font>

403
00:20:03,660 --> 00:20:05,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hugh? What is it?</font>

404
00:20:06,960 --> 00:20:09,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry. I have blood on me right now.</font>

405
00:20:09,510 --> 00:20:10,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all right.</font>

406
00:20:11,140 --> 00:20:14,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I started thinking of such 
scum's blood as wastewater,</font>

407
00:20:14,560 --> 00:20:16,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got a little better with it.</font>

408
00:20:16,660 --> 00:20:19,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's a very Hugh-like 
way of getting over it.</i></font>

409
00:20:19,830 --> 00:20:22,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what's going on?</font>

410
00:20:22,080 --> 00:20:23,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

411
00:20:24,660 --> 00:20:27,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mike-kun, is there 
anything I can help with?</font>

412
00:20:28,280 --> 00:20:32,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There is, but... they 
entrusted this job to me.</font>

413
00:20:32,840 --> 00:20:34,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. So...</font>

414
00:20:37,140 --> 00:20:38,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">won't you let me do it with you?</font>

415
00:20:38,990 --> 00:20:42,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then, I'd like it if you 
helped me with mine.</font>

416
00:20:42,880 --> 00:20:46,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We still can't do this like 
Siu-san and the others can,</font>

417
00:20:46,520 --> 00:20:48,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but with the two of us together, 
we'll get a little closer!</font>

418
00:20:52,220 --> 00:20:55,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right! Let's get this 
taken care of quick, together!</font>

419
00:20:55,550 --> 00:20:56,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's do it!</font>

420
00:20:58,780 --> 00:21:00,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're done, too?</font>

421
00:21:00,480 --> 00:21:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, but we ended up working together.</font>

422
00:21:03,580 --> 00:21:04,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

423
00:21:04,830 --> 00:21:06,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What're you apologizing for?</font>

424
00:21:07,140 --> 00:21:09,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You decided to work together 
and made it through, right?</font>

425
00:21:09,900 --> 00:21:11,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Job well done!</font>

426
00:21:11,650 --> 00:21:15,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The way you two work so well 
together is a powerful weapon.</font>

427
00:21:15,030 --> 00:21:15,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did good.</font>

428
00:21:16,180 --> 00:21:18,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were rough assignments 
to handle alone.</font>

429
00:21:18,910 --> 00:21:19,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

430
00:21:19,930 --> 00:21:21,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hela-san can be so mean.</font>

431
00:21:22,100 --> 00:21:24,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a bad habit of his.</font>

432
00:21:24,210 --> 00:21:26,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Hela was sure that we'd be 
able to handle this job now,</font>

433
00:21:26,800 --> 00:21:28,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and that's why he took it.</font>

434
00:21:29,090 --> 00:21:31,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Meaning you two are
counted as valuable assets.</font>

435
00:21:33,590 --> 00:21:37,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So we've already become 
splendid master torturers?</font>

436
00:21:37,720 --> 00:21:38,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, now.</font>

437
00:21:38,640 --> 00:21:40,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just a joke.</font>

438
00:21:40,780 --> 00:21:43,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, we want to catch up 
to Sero-san and Siu-san!</font>

439
00:21:43,840 --> 00:21:45,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right, Hugh?</font>

440
00:21:45,020 --> 00:21:45,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

441
00:21:46,060 --> 00:21:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As individuals, that's one thing,</font>

442
00:21:47,880 --> 00:21:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but as a duo, I think you two 
might have already beaten us.</font>

443
00:21:51,400 --> 00:21:54,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't be serious! 
We're the strongest team, aren't we?</font>

444
00:21:54,680 --> 00:21:55,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are we?</font>

445
00:21:55,720 --> 00:21:57,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please continue to mentor us!</font>

446
00:21:57,980 --> 00:21:59,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please do!</font>

447
00:21:59,260 --> 00:22:00,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure thing!</font>

448
00:22:01,150 --> 00:22:03,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be counting on you!</font>

449
00:22:03,600 --> 00:22:05,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

450
00:22:04,470 --> 00:22:06,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Seriously. I'm depending on you.</font>

451
00:22:06,040 --> 00:22:07,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll work my very hardest.</font>

452
00:22:06,260 --> 00:22:08,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Okay! Let's all grab something to eat!</font>

453
